---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="Ramesh Dewan to Build New Hotel at Luton Airport - Creating Job Opportunities"
    description="Major hotel development at Luton Airport by property investor Ramesh Dewan will create hundreds of jobs in hospitality, construction, and management sectors."
    keywords="Luton Airport hotel, Ramesh Dewan, hospitality jobs, hotel careers, construction jobs, Luton employment, career opportunities, hospitality sector"
    section="jobs-and-careers"
>
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-purple-800 text-white py-12">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
                    Ramesh Dewan to Build New Hotel at Luton Airport
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-purple-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                    Major development project creates significant job opportunities in hospitality and construction sectors
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <nav class="bg-gray-50 py-4" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
                <li>
                    <a href="/" class="hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors">Home</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.293 14.707a1 1 0 010-1.414L10.586 10 7.293 6.707a1 1 0 111.414-1.414l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/jobs-and-careers" class="hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors">Jobs and Careers</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.293 14.707a1 1 0 010-1.414L10.586 10 7.293 6.707a1 1 0 111.414-1.414l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/jobs-and-careers/career-sectors" class="hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors">Career Sectors</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.293 14.707a1 1 0 010-1.414L10.586 10 7.293 6.707a1 1 0 111.414-1.414l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                </li>
                <li class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Hotel Development News</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <section class="py-12 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
                <!-- Article Meta -->
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                        <div>
                            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-purple-100 text-purple-800">
                                Business Development
                            </span>
                            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 ml-2">
                                Job Creation
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                            Published: July 2025
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Introduction -->
                <div class="bg-purple-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Major Hotel Development at Luton Airport</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
                        Property investor and developer Ramesh Dewan has announced plans to build a major new hotel complex at Luton Airport, creating hundreds of job opportunities across multiple sectors including hospitality, construction, and management.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Main Content -->
                <div class="space-y-8">
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Project Overview</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                            The ambitious development project, led by renowned property investor Ramesh Dewan, represents a significant investment in the Luton area's hospitality infrastructure. The new hotel complex will cater to the growing demand from business travelers and tourists using Luton Airport, which has seen substantial passenger growth in recent years.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                            "This development represents not just an investment in bricks and mortar, but in the local community and economy," stated Dewan. "We're committed to creating quality employment opportunities while meeting the increasing demand for accommodation near the airport."
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Job Creation Opportunities</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                            The hotel development is expected to create a significant number of employment opportunities across various phases of the project:
                        </p>
                        
                        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Construction Phase Jobs</h3>
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                                <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg">
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Direct Employment</h4>
                                    <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-1">
                                        <li>• Construction workers</li>
                                        <li>• Site managers</li>
                                        <li>• Engineers</li>
                                        <li>• Electricians and plumbers</li>
                                        <li>• Health and safety officers</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg">
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Support Services</h4>
                                    <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-1">
                                        <li>• Architects and designers</li>
                                        <li>• Project coordinators</li>
                                        <li>• Environmental consultants</li>
                                        <li>• Legal and planning advisors</li>
                                        <li>• Transport and logistics</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Operational Phase Jobs</h3>
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                                <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg">
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Management</h4>
                                    <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-1">
                                        <li>• General Manager</li>
                                        <li>• Department Heads</li>
                                        <li>• HR Manager</li>
                                        <li>• Finance Manager</li>
                                        <li>• Sales & Marketing</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg">
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Guest Services</h4>
                                    <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-1">
                                        <li>• Reception staff</li>
                                        <li>• Concierge services</li>
                                        <li>• Guest relations</li>
                                        <li>• Reservations team</li>
                                        <li>• Night auditors</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg">
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Operations</h4>
                                    <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-1">
                                        <li>• Housekeeping staff</li>
                                        <li>• Maintenance team</li>
                                        <li>• Security personnel</li>
                                        <li>• F&B service staff</li>
                                        <li>• Kitchen staff</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Economic Impact</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                            The development is expected to have a substantial positive impact on the local economy. Industry experts estimate that the hotel will:
                        </p>
                        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                                <div class="text-center">
                                    <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">300+</div>
                                    <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Construction jobs during build phase</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-center">
                                    <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">150+</div>
                                    <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Permanent hospitality positions</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-center">
                                    <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">£2M+</div>
                                    <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Annual local economic contribution</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Skills and Training Opportunities</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                            Recognizing the importance of developing local talent, Ramesh Dewan's development company has committed to implementing comprehensive training programs:
                        </p>
                        
                        <div class="space-y-4">
                            <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-600 pl-4">
                                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Apprenticeship Programs</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Partnerships with local colleges to offer hospitality and construction apprenticeships</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-600 pl-4">
                                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Professional Development</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Ongoing training for staff in customer service, management, and specialized skills</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-600 pl-4">
                                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Graduate Schemes</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Management trainee programs for university graduates entering the hospitality sector</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-600 pl-4">
                                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Career Progression</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Clear pathways for advancement within the organization</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Local Community Benefits</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                            Beyond direct employment, the hotel development is expected to bring numerous benefits to the local community:
                        </p>
                        
                        <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Community Impact</h3>
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Economic Benefits</h4>
                                    <ul class="text-gray-700 text-sm space-y-1">
                                        <li>• Increased local spending</li>
                                        <li>• Support for local suppliers</li>
                                        <li>• Business rate contributions</li>
                                        <li>• Tourism revenue growth</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Social Benefits</h4>
                                    <ul class="text-gray-700 text-sm space-y-1">
                                        <li>• Community meeting spaces</li>
                                        <li>• Local hiring preferences</li>
                                        <li>• Youth employment initiatives</li>
                                        <li>• Environmental improvements</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Career Opportunities in Hospitality</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                            This development highlights the growing opportunities in the hospitality sector. For those considering a career in hospitality, the industry offers:
                        </p>
                        
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                            <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Entry-Level Opportunities</h3>
                                <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                                    <li class="flex items-start">
                                        <span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">•</span>
                                        No experience required for many positions
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start">
                                        <span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">•</span>
                                        On-the-job training provided
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start">
                                        <span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">•</span>
                                        Flexible working hours
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start">
                                        <span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">•</span>
                                        Customer service skills development
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Career Progression</h3>
                                <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                                    <li class="flex items-start">
                                        <span class="text-green-600 mr-2">•</span>
                                        Clear advancement pathways
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start">
                                        <span class="text-green-600 mr-2">•</span>
                                        International career opportunities
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start">
                                        <span class="text-green-600 mr-2">•</span>
                                        Management development programs
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start">
                                        <span class="text-green-600 mr-2">•</span>
                                        Competitive salary progression
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Timeline -->
                    <div class="bg-purple-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Development Timeline</h2>
                        <div class="space-y-4">
                            <div class="flex items-start">
                                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold mr-4 mt-1">1</div>
                                <div>
                                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Planning & Design Phase</h3>
                                    <p class="text-gray-700">Finalization of architectural plans and securing necessary permits</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start">
                                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold mr-4 mt-1">2</div>
                                <div>
                                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Construction Commencement</h3>
                                    <p class="text-gray-700">Breaking ground and beginning of major construction work</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start">
                                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold mr-4 mt-1">3</div>
                                <div>
                                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Recruitment Drive</h3>
                                    <p class="text-gray-700">Beginning of recruitment for operational staff and management</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start">
                                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold mr-4 mt-1">4</div>
                                <div>
                                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Grand Opening</h3>
                                    <p class="text-gray-700">Hotel opens to guests with full operational capacity</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Quote Section -->
                    <div class="bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-purple-600 p-6 my-8">
                        <blockquote class="text-lg text-gray-700 italic">
                            "This project demonstrates our commitment to investing in infrastructure that not only serves travelers but also creates meaningful employment opportunities for local communities. We believe in building for the future while supporting the present."
                        </blockquote>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">- Ramesh Dewan, Property Developer</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- How to Apply -->
                    <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">How to Apply for Opportunities</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                            As the project progresses, job opportunities will be advertised through various channels:
                        </p>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                            <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded">
                                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Construction Phase</h3>
                                <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-1">
                                    <li>• Main contractor recruitment portals</li>
                                    <li>• Local job centers</li>
                                    <li>• Construction industry websites</li>
                                    <li>• Trade union announcements</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded">
                                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Hotel Operations</h3>
                                <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-1">
                                    <li>• Hotel company website</li>
                                    <li>• Hospitality job boards</li>
                                    <li>• Local recruitment fairs</li>
                                    <li>• Partner college placements</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <!-- Related Articles -->
            <section class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Related Career Articles</h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                            <a href="/jobs-and-careers/career-sectors/7599-what-does-a-solicitor-do" class="hover:text-purple-600">Legal Career Opportunities</a>
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Understanding career paths in the legal sector and required qualifications.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                            <a href="/jobs-and-careers/career-sectors/7953-uk-graduates-flock-to-china-for-job-opportunities" class="hover:text-purple-600">International Opportunities</a>
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">How UK graduates are finding success in global job markets.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                            <a href="/jobs-and-careers/job-search" class="hover:text-purple-600">Job Search Strategies</a>
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Expert tips and advice for finding your ideal career opportunity.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                            <a href="/jobs-and-careers/career-sectors" class="hover:text-purple-600">Explore Career Sectors</a>
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Discover opportunities across different industries and sectors.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Call to Action -->
            <section class="mt-12 bg-purple-600 text-white p-8 rounded-lg">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Stay Updated on Job Opportunities</h2>
                    <p class="text-purple-100 mb-6">
                        Register with us to receive notifications about new job openings in hospitality, construction, and other growing sectors.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
                        <a 
                            href="/jobs-and-careers/job-search/7651-job-vacancy-form"
                            class="bg-white text-purple-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-purple-50 transition-colors"
                        >
                            Register for Job Alerts
                        </a>
                        <a 
                            href="/jobs-and-careers/career-sectors"
                            class="border-2 border-white text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors"
                        >
                            Browse Career Sectors
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>